75395.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
75395.description: The gang leaves the Fire Nation, humbled and embarrassed by the failure of the invasion. They head to the Western Air Temple. However, unknown to them, Zuko is also following them in the hope of joining their group to teach Aang firebending.

75396.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
75396.description: Aang is ready to start his firebending training. However, as Zuko attempts to teach him, he realizes he has lost all his firebending power; as he is no longer drawing his firebending power from rage, anger and his desire to capture Aang. They journey to find the true source of firebending.

75397.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75397.description: Plankton disguises himself as SpongeBob’s grandmother. // Mr. Krabs uses Gary to find spare change.

75398.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75398.description: A monster terrorizes Bikini Bottom until Patrick befriends the huge creature. // SpongeBob and all the Bikini Bottom citizens disappear to an underwater resort.

75399.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
75399.description: When Raph makes a new friend in Zog, an alien Triceraton, he may have bitten off more than he can chew.

75400.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
75400.description: When the Turtles get word of the Kraang's return, they realize there is an even bigger threat coming to Earth!

75401.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
75401.description: Po befriends a band of dancers, unaware they're actually a band of traveling thieves.

75402.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
75402.description: When the Furious 5 are all out of town and the Jade Palace is attacked, Po only has his dad and two old people to help him.

75403.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
75403.description: A little girl loses her doll at the zoo, and Rico gives up his own doll to replace it. Private assures Rico that his good deed will come back to him. // When a raccoon shows up and starts stealing from the zoo animals, the penguins jump into action.

75404.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
75404.description: The penguins’ dolphin nemesis, Dr. Blowhole, is out for revenge. After Blowhole takes King Julien hostage, Skipper and gang must rush to rescue their annoying neighbor and stop evil Dr. Blowhole before he destroys the planet.

75405.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75405.description: Pearl's getting ready for her slumber party, but Mr. Krabs' meddling in the party preparations is getting out of control. // SpongeBob decides to enter Gary in a pet show and gives him a makeover after seeing the competition.

75406.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75406.description: SpongeBob and his friends are swept away by a giant wave and find themselves stranded on a remote tropical island. To get back to Bikini Bottom, they need to learn how to surf from enigmatic surf guru, Jack Kahuna Lagun.

75407.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75407.description: When SpongeBob suddenly becomes the richest citizen of Bikini Bottom, he finds himself surrounded by lots of new "friends" who are more than happy to help him spend his money. // It's the day of Squidward's big lead solo audition with the Bikini Bottom Men's Chorus, and Squidward is brimming with excitement. He's positive he's a shoo-in for the part.

75409.title: Nella The Princess Knight
75409.description: Nella and Trinket accidently agree to attend both Garrett and Minatori's sleepovers on the same night. // Garrett and Blaine disobey the rules and sneak out at night to see a fantastical star.

75410.title: Nella The Princess Knight
75410.description: Blaine's fancy cousin Olivia visits and questions Nella's ability to be both a princess and a knight. // When Nella loses a knightly contest, she's determined to improve by practicing.

75411.title: Bubble Guppies
75411.description: Rawrrrrrr! While the Bubble Guppies are digging for dinosaur bones, they learn all about different types of dinosaurs.

75412.title: Bubble Guppies
75412.description: To celebrate Shrimptennial, the Bubble Guppies visit Big Bubble City! Join them in discovering the hustle and bustle of the big city and the Big Bubble Building!

75413.title: Dora the Explorer
75413.description: Hic! Boom! Ohhhh!!! What's that funny sound coming from Yellow Valley? Dora and Boots set off to investigate. They'll have to go across the Noisy River, then tiptoe through the Quiet Forest, and that's how they'll get there.

75414.title: Dora the Explorer
75414.description: Dora brings Boots a special present, a new floaty that will help him swim. Boots is thrilled, and they set off for the beach. But first they'll have to go through the Dune maze (watch out for the crabs!), then fix the broken Boardwalk, and that's how they'll get to the beach.

75415.title: Rusty Rivets
75415.description: Rusty builds his Mom the ultimate relaxing chair, but whenever it hears any noise, it runs away and raises high into the sky! // Rusty, and Ruby try to save the Wake Up and Smell the Roses Contest from Frankie Fritz' stinky Robotic Skunk.

75416.title: Rusty Rivets
75416.description: When Liam gets trapped atop a tall stack of junk with his stuffed dinosaur, Rusty designs a Jurassic rescue. // When Mr. Higgins' remote control plane won't land, Rusty and the gang must bring it down safely - using Crush as a daredevil rescue pilot hero!

75417.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
75417.description: Blaze and his driver AJ are introduced to a world of racing Monster Machines. But when a truck named Crusher uses tricks to try and win the Championship Race, Blaze will do everything he can to help his friends and beat Crusher to the finish line.

75418.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
75418.description: Blaze and his driver AJ are introduced to a world of racing Monster Machines. But when a truck named Crusher uses dirty tricks to try and win the Championship Race, Blaze will do everything he can to help his friends and beat Crusher to the finish line.

75419.title: PAW Patrol
75419.description: Cap’n Turbot and his cousin Francois are whale watching when the Flounder hits a rock and starts to sink! This rescue needs all paws on deck. // Stowaway penguins have scattered around Adventure Bay! Time to call the PAW Patrol!

75420.title: PAW Patrol
75420.description: Jake and Everest are excited for the Snowboard Competition, until they see the course is buried under a blanket of snow. // When the PAW Patrol sets out to retrieve Cap'n Turbot's sunken diving bell, they meet a giant Sea Slug!

75421.title: PAW Patrol
75421.description: Alex and Mr. Porter are delivering pizza dough for a big party when the van spins out of control. Pups to the rescue! // Skye is on her way to Jake's Mountain when she crash lands in the snow. Ryder calls Everest to save the day!

75422.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75422.description: It's summer break, and Mr. Krabs wants to squeeze every penny out of the children who are out of school. He takes a pile of rusty old junk and concocts a playground of sorts. // SpongeBob and Patrick decide to go camping…in the back yard. Squidward comes out to tell them to be quiet, but takes their innocent "have fun inside the house" comment as a challenge.

75423.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75423.description: SpongeBob has lost his name tag! He has no idea where it has gone. He retraces all of his steps, with "help" from Patrick, but to no avail. // It is the 25th anniversary of Plankton's first attempt to steal the Krabby Patty Secret Formula. The entire Krusty Krab crew is on its guard, and foils Plankton at every turn.

75424.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75424.description: SpongeBob is jellyfishing when he realizes that he wants to fly with the jellyfish. He proceeds to come up with numerous ways to fly. He and Patrick try everything from constructing a plane to tying SpongeBob to a kite.

75425.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
75425.description: King Julien's archrival, Clemson, returns in another attempt to claim the lemur crown. This time the sneaky lemur has a document that "proves" King Julien is not the legitimate king because he wasn't born in Madagascar. A series of challenges to prove who's more kingly ensues, and the penguins try to stack the deck in Julien's favor by each switching brains with him. Simple, right? How could a plan like this possibly fail? Private and the Winky Factory: Private's favorite treat, the Peanut Butter Winky, is going the way of the dinosaur. Distraught that the snack cake is ceasing production, Private urges a raid on the Winky Factory where the last remaining Winkies are rolling off the production line. Impressed by Private's passion, Skipper gives him command of the mission! The young penguin learns there's a heck of a lot to digest when leading a team.

75426.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
75426.description: Kowalski invents an enemy detector. As is often the case, it doesn't work, and Skipper gets his own wires crossed when he smashes it. Old enemies are now friends and old friends are now enemies as the boss bird starts to systematically clean out the zoo with the help of his new friend Hans. King Julien gets into the act by becoming Skipper's friend too, going so far as to Congaga dance together. New BFF Hans is not happy with the new bromance, however. Could this be the opening the penguins need? // The annual Zoo Snooze is here! Kids get to buy tickets for a zoo sleepover, a treat the animals look forward to every year! This year's going to be very different, however, when the rotten Vesuvius Twins buy up all the tickets themselves. The zoosters plan to turn the tables, though, and exact sweet revenge on the twins. The penguins, influenced by Private of course, can't let this happen, and it's a long night's journey into day as the penguins scramble to protect their one-time tormentors.

75427.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
75427.description: After Po gets trapped in a hole, Fung helps him out and is owed a favor. Will it be a costly one?

75428.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
75428.description: To impress his fan club, Po releases the Mongolian Fist Demon. Now he has to figure out how to defeat the Demon and save the village and his fans!

75429.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
75429.description: Facing Shredder's deadly new assassin, Leo must decide whether to risk his brother's lives or ask for Splinter's help. Donnie must put aside his rivalry with Casey in order to uncover a new Kraang plot.

75430.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
75430.description: Facing Shredder's deadly new assassin, Leo must decide whether to risk his brother's lives or ask for Splinter's help. Donnie must put aside his rivalry with Casey in order to uncover a new Kraang plot.

75431.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75431.description: SpongeBob wants to be the first sponge to dive all the way up to the surface of the ocean! // When SpongeBob and Squidward accidentally let Plankton steal the secret formula, it's up to them to steal it back!

75432.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75432.description: Now that Fred's leg has healed up, SpongeBob is determined to keep it out of harm's way...no matter what! // Patrick's lemonade stand isn't doing too well...until he gets a secret ingredient from Squidward!

75433.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75433.description: When The Krusty Krab runs out of mustard, Mr. Krabs sends SpongeBob, Patrick and Squidward to dig up some more! // SpongeBob and Sandy have to collect Krabby Patty ingredients, but Plankton is following their every step.

75434.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
75434.description: A rash of thefts in the Valley of Peace has the villagers in uproar and things only get worse when the culprit appears to be... Monkey?

75435.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
75435.description: Po's Kung Fu hero, Kwan the Unkillable, comes to the Valley of Peace and appears to be a feeble old man. Po agrees to stage a fight to help him get back on top. But Kwan may not be as weak as he looks.

75436.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
75436.description: Julien is horrified when the baboons' dance routine gets more attention than his own. His attempts to sabotage the baboons blow up in his face. // There's a blackout and Julien convinces everyone they should revert to "jungle law" with him as king.

75437.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
75437.description: After an injury, Skipper goes to the vet for treatment. The rest of the team thinks he has turned into a zombie. // A hive of hornets has appeared at the entrance, and they refuse to leave. The penguins must find a way to dispose of the hornets.

75438.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
75438.description: When the Turtles get word of the Kraang's return, they realize there is an even bigger threat coming to Earth!

75439.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
75439.description: When Shredder teams with the Kraang to receive a batch of mutagen, the Turtles' problems only get worse-even putting their friendship with April at stake.

75440.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75440.description: Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy are eating at the Krusty Krab when Mermaid Man accidentally drops his utility belt. SpongeBob finds the belt and can’t resist it. // During a boating lesson with Mrs. Puff, SpongeBob loses control of his boat and crashes it into a juice truck and a senior citizens home. Mrs. Puff confesses that she is responsible for SpongeBob, so the police throw her in jail.

75441.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75441.description: When it snows in Bikini Bottom, SpongeBob and Pat go out in the snow and play in their snow forts etc… They make a racket and Squid complains. Squid makes fun of them for playing in the snow. // When Mr. Krabs has a garage sale and tries to sell everyone’s trash as priceless heirlooms, he ends up selling Spongebob a novelty soda drink hat, which to Krabs’s surprise turns out to be the most popular item in Bikini Bottom.

75442.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75442.description: Krabs makes a low budget commercial and SpongeBob is in it for one second. After the commercial airs once at three in the morning, a blind man recognizes SpongeBob. // Squid is fed up with Krab’s insults and he quits, bragging about how easy it will be to find another job. But of course, it’s not and Squid falls upon hard times. He goes though all his savings and is dirt poor.

75443.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
75443.description: Master Chao visits the valley to oversee a Tournament. Shifu is convinced that Po and Master Chao want to replace him. Shifu's old enemy, Pai Mei, arrives in the middle of the tournament and threatens to destroy Shifu.

75444.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
75444.description: Master Yao returns to the Jade Palace and announces that he's offering the Valley of Peace a one-day 'Wonder and Wisdom Exchange'. Anyone who brings him a new wonder will be allowed to ask him a single question.

75445.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
75445.description: When Skipper is knocked on the head, he's unable to lead the penguins on an important mission. The team scrambles to take his place, but they each have a hard time filling Skippers flippers./Private accidentally drinks Kowalski's truth serum and starts spilling the penguin's secrets to the rest of the zoo. Worst of all, he reveals they have been spying on their neighbors!

75446.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
75446.description: The lemurs argue, and Maurice and Mort move out of the habitat. Lonely Julien starts bugging the penguins, who decide they must get the lemurs back together. // A tiny frog with a nasty attitude moves to the zoo and starts terrorizing the animals.

75447.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
75447.description: Sokka and Zuko break into The Boiling Rock Prison, the Fire Nation's highest security prison, to rescue Hakoda. When they develope an escape plan after finding Hakoda not there, other prisoners get involved and ruin it. Now the two, and a recently discovered Suki have to find another way out of the inescapable fortress.

75448.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
75448.description: This episode is continuing the jailbreak from the previous episode. Sokka, Hakoda, Zuko and Suki form a new escape plan, but it is complicated by the arrival of Princess Azula. In a desparate bid for freedom, the four escape due to the assitance of Mai.

75449.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75449.description: SpongeBob and Sandy are enjoying a day at the beach when they come across the Salty Spitoon, a rough and tumble hangout for real rugged folk. Sandy makes it through the bouncer, but SpongeBob is left outside. // Squidward's arch nemesis, Squilliam, has returned to harass Squidward on his failed life since high school. Squidward lies and tells him that he actually owns a five star restaurant.

75450.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75450.description: SpongeBob and Patrick are wreaking havoc on the Krusty Krab, so Mr. Krabs decides to give them a little busy work. He tells them to paint his living room, and gives them permanent paint. Very permanent. // The excitement! You are now a member of the official Krusty Krab crew! In this informative episode, you will learn all of the attributes necessary to become an excellent employee in the world of fast food restaurants.

75451.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75451.description: SpongeBob, while grocery shopping, discovers a "how to throw a party" kit. He decides to throw a big party and invites everyone he's ever known. Unfortunately for his guests, SpongeBob plans everything right down to the minute.

75452.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
75452.description: When the Turtles face Shredder's newest threat, an army of Robot Foot Soldiers, Karai captures Leonardo and forces him to do battle with these new and improved ninjas that can adapt to his every move.

75453.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
75453.description: While tracking mutagen, the Turtles bring a mutated squirrel back to the lair. When it starts multiplying, the Turtles must hunt the squirrel mutants and prevent them escaping into the city.

75454.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
75454.description: Po saves a girl from some bandits, only to learn that she's engaged to be married to the Dragon Warrior.

75455.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
75455.description: During a fight with Tong Fo, Po is struck by lightning, giving him the power to read minds.

75456.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
75456.description: When Burt the elephant asks the penguins to help him sneak out of the zoo, they take on the challenge and get the big guy out. // Marlene catches a glimpse of Fred the squirrel and falls in love at first sight.

75457.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
75457.description: When Alice mentions that one of the penguins is actually female, Skipper has an identity crisis. It’s up to Marlene to convince him that he can still be a commando, even if he’s a girl... // After a big fight Mason moves out—and in with the penguins. Unfortunately, Mason is a very annoying house guest. The penguins must figure out a way to get the chimps to make up before Mason drives them all bananas.

75458.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
75458.description: Kowalski accidentally creates a living blob of jelly. But "Jiggles" has a big appetite and starts stealing fruit from the animals. // When a new TV show starts keeping people from coming to the zoo, the animals worry they'll lose their home.

75459.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75459.description: SpongeBob and Pat want to make some extra cash so they decide to sell chocolate bars door to door. They have no luck at first. In fact, they end up buying more stuff than selling stuff. // Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy are visiting the Krusty Krab, and they get into an argument about whether or not Barnacle boy should be treated as the kid sidekick anymore.

75460.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75460.description: It's another day of boating school for SpongeBob, and this time, Patrick wants to come along too. Patrick becomes the new student in SpongeBob's class, and from his introduction, begins getting SpongeBob in trouble. // It's another day at the Krusty Krab when a random customer makes a purchase that causes Mr. Krabs to earn his one millionth dollar! To celebrate, he takes SpongeBob and Squidward on a clam fishing trip.

75461.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75461.description: It is prehistoric Bikini Bottom, and we spend a day in the life of SpongeGar, Patar, and Squog. Thanks to the magic of an underwater thunderstorm, our three Neanderthal friends discover fire.
